title: Dementia 2
overview: Acclaimed director and certified lunatic Jim Powers returns to the Land of Dementia. Once again, an innocent girl is cast into a bizarre world of fetish and anal sex. Dementia #2 is so weird, so perverse and so twisted, that mere words can't begin to describe it. With a star-studded cast of cock-crazy madwomen and the freakiest sex imaginable, you're going to think you're suffering from Dementia of your own.
